title: Live Show Tonight!
description:
Tonight, Thursday, May 12th, is Bitch Sesh Live from Home Spring Fling! Get tickets at LoopedLive.com or find the link through Casey's (@caseyrosewilson) and Danielle's (@daniellecarolineschneider) Instagram! 

It’s the premiere of the new season of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and the end of this season of Jersey (Sunrise, Sunset), so of course, we all need to bear witness to this important time together. Get your jammies and your drink on and join Casey, Danielle and their hilarious guests for a Bitch Sesh live (from home) show you don’t want to miss.
author: bwordsesh@gmail.com (Earwolf)
